Today I am sorry I won’t be able to cover all the centers

01:04:38.577 --> 01:04:42.846
because its already quite late and we have this hall only till 10:30.

01:04:43.046 --> 01:04:47.917
So we have to do the actualization of the experience

01:04:48.117 --> 01:04:51.143
of getting the realization and we have to work it out.

01:04:51.343 --> 01:04:54.865
So that is the main thing and whatever was possible I have told you

01:04:55.065 --> 01:04:59.081
the theory behind the awakening of the Kundalini up to these centers

01:04:59.281 --> 01:05:03.724
and if possible tomorrow I will try to do the other two centers.

01:05:03.924 --> 01:05:09.142
Now should we have the experience?

01:05:17.888 --> 01:05:20.579
I think it would be better if everyone moves forward,

01:05:20.779 --> 01:05:24.302
will be better for us to work it out.

