01:07:49.651 --> 01:07:54.690
and develop your powers, your own powers,

01:07:54.901 --> 01:07:57.912
and master it

01:07:58.112 --> 01:08:00.943
so that you start giving realization to others.

01:08:01.143 --> 01:08:03.221
You all can do it.

