In the beginning what happens is that,

01:08:08.486 --> 01:08:13.682
like anything, any light which you enlightened is rather difficult.

01:08:13.883 --> 01:08:15.254
You have to look after it.

01:08:15.454 --> 01:08:17.989
Any seed that has sprouted, the seedling

